results.description: Travelling with your partner can have its ups and downs, and sometimes it can be tough to get a lot of lovely shots together! I love this image of us together; I set it up using manual adjustments on the camera, and a stranger kindly pointed and shot for me as we looked out to the famous Sigiriya Rock in Sri Lanka because I only have a small gorilla tripod. This is definitely an up moment, I loved just gazing together with my partner out at Sigiriya after hiking and scrambling to the top of nearby Pindurangala Rock.
